  <brief_title>Decreased Consumption of Blood Components During Cardiac Surgery Procedures: Causes and Effects.</brief_title>
  <official_title>Decreased Consumption of Blood Components During Cardiac Surgery Procedures: Causes and Effects.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
